flowchart TD
    A[New process arrives] --> B[Queue 1]
    B --> C{Finished within Q1?}
    C -- Yes --> D[Complete process]
    C -- No --> E[Demote to Queue 2]
    E --> F{Finished within Q2?}
    F -- Yes --> D
    F -- No --> G[Demote to Queue 3]
    G --> H[Run third-level policy]
    H --> I{Finished?}
    I -- Yes --> D
    I -- No --> G
